          <div class="col-md-12 gx-5 mb-4">
            <h4><strong>About Us</strong></h4>
            <p class="text-muted">
              JUSense is a team of enthusiastic members on a mission to utilise state-of-the-art artificial intelligence for societal benefits.
              We focus on basic and advansed research in a multitude of areas including IoT-Cloud, Social Network Analysis and Geoinformatics.
